title.rendered: 500 x Patient HDPE 720 x 470mm Clothing Bag with Draw String  – Blue PTD

content.rendered:
Patient Clothing Bag is made of high-quality HDPE and features Patient Clothing Print to easily identify. This clothing bag has a drawstring for ease of closure.

  • Blue PTD
  • HDPE material
  • EPI
  • Suitable for use in hospitals
  • 720mm x 470mm
  • 20 packs of 25
